OL,3,CPensioner accused of murdering her 84-
OL,4,Cyear-old husband appears in court
OL,6,FA woman has appeared in court charged
OL,7,Fwith murdering her 84-year-old husband.
OL,9,FDaryl Berman, 70, is accused of
OL,10,Fmurdering her husband David Berman,
OL,11,Fwho was found dead at his home on
OL,12,FButterstile Lane in Prestwich in March.
OL,14,FDaryl Berman was charged with his
OL,15,Fmurder by Greater Manchester Police on
OL,16,FMonday 9 June.
OL,18,FMrs Berman, of Butterstile Lane,
OL,19,Fappeared before magistrates Tuesday 10
OL,20,FJune.
