OL,3,CPensioner accused of murdering her 84-
OL,4,Cyear-old husband appears in court
OL,6,FShe re-appeared at Minshull Street
OL,7,FCrown Court in Manchester via
OL,8,Fvideolink from HMP Styal on Wednesday
OL,9,F11 June for a preliminary hearing and
OL,10,Fmade no application for bail.
OL,12,FHer barrister Michael Hayton KC
OL,13,Fconfirmed a bail application is to be
OL,14,Fmade in due course. Prosecutor Simon
OL,15,FBarrett confirmed the case was to
OL,16,Fproceed to a trial later in the year.
