OL,3,CPensioner accused of murdering her 84-
OL,4,Cyear-old husband appears in court
OL,6,FJudge Maurice Greene adjourned the
OL,7,Fcase until 9 September for a pre-trial
OL,8,Fhearing. A trial due to last between
OL,9,Ffive and seven days is scheduled to
OL,10,Fbegin on 8 December.
OL,12,FMrs Berman was remanded in custody. No
OL,13,Fpleas were entered.
OL,15,FNeighbours described Mr Berman, who
OL,16,Fhad lived on the street for several
OL,17,Fdecades, as a 'lovely man' with a 'big
OL,18,Fheart' and said he was a joiner who
OL,19,Fhad only recently retired.
