OL,3,CPensioner accused of murdering her 84-
OL,4,Cyear-old husband appears in court
OL,6,FOne said: "He was a nice guy. I would
OL,7,Fsee him going up and down the street
OL,8,Fto get his paper. I would have a craic
OL,9,Fwith him.
OL,11,F"It's a bit of a shock. I just can't
OL,12,Fbelieve it. It's not something you
OL,13,Fexpect to happen on your doorstep."
OL,15,FAnother said: "He was a lovely, well-
OL,16,Fmannered gentleman. He seemed like he
OL,17,Fhad a big heart. When we moved in, he
OL,18,Fwas the first to come and say hello
OL,19,Fand see if we were okay.
