OL,6,F"He was just a really nice person. He
OL,7,Fwouldn't say anything bad about
OL,8,Fanybody. He was a carpenter, and he
OL,9,Fonly retired last year, which goes to
OL,10,Fshow what he was like. It's a big
OL,11,Fshock."
